ActCanadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety Act
PrecisAppointment of ROSS WILLIAM NAIRNE of Edmonton, Alberta, to be a governor of the Council of the Canadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety, being the nominee of the Lieutenant Governor in Council of the Province of Alberta, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years.
